-- Alfa Bank Employees Receive No 2011 Bonus, Finparty Reports
-- B y   J a c k   J o r d a n
-- 2012-04-26T18:46:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-26/alfa-bank-employees-receive-no-2011-bonus-finparty-reports.html
Alfa Bank’s board decided employees
in its investment-banking division will not receive a bonus for
2011, Finparty reported, citing unidentified workers at  Russia ’s
largest private lender.  Finparty, a Russian-language financial news website,
interviewed ten employees of the company about bonus payments,
it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
